Synopsis:

This scripts is used for detecting bias in duplication direction,
by switching left and right duplications one at a time.


Usage:
>AllscrumbleDupBias.pl  MapsFileinFasta CostFile NoOfIterations 
                        NameofTempFiles arlem_in_full_path

Note: NameofTempFile indicated the prefix of temporary files 
      generated. These files store the scrumbled sequences and
      their alignment.  

      NoOfIterations: are the number of iterations for scrumble test 
      (50 is reasonable)

Destination Directories:
      Output is reported in the directory where sequence file exist.
      The temporary files are stored anywhere according to the given path